msgstr "僅顯示您添加到以下清單中的播放器"

#: prefs.js:569
msgid "Saved Players"
msgstr "已儲存的播放器"

#: prefs.js:571
msgid ""
"Each saved player can be individually enabled or disabled in the filter "
