msgstr "免費開源的時間同步歌詞資料庫 — 無需註冊，不追蹤，無廣告"

#: prefs.js:1120
msgid "Privacy note"
msgstr "隱私說明"

#: prefs.js:1122
msgid ""
"A request containing the track title, artist, album and duration is sent to "
