#: prefs.js:2646
msgid ""
"• Multi-instance browser support\n"
"• Per-app rotating vinyl record album art\n"
"• Animated tonearm\n"
"• Smooth animations\n"
"• Double-click to toggle vinyl per app\n"
"• Triple-click album art to show synced lyrics\n"
"• Single-click lyrics panel to return to album art\n"
"• Lyrics synced to playback via lrclib.net\n"
"• Per-player lyrics toggle (each tab independent)\n"
"• All seen apps remembered — re-enable any time"
msgstr ""
"• 多重實例瀏覽器支援\n"
"• 每個應用程式的旋轉黑膠專輯封面\n"
"• 動態唱臂\n"
"• 流暢動畫\n"
"• 雙擊可切換每個應用程式的黑膠\n"
"• 三擊專輯封面顯示同步歌詞\n"
"• 單擊歌詞面板返回專輯封面\n"
"• 歌詞透過 lrclib.net 與播放同步\n"
"• 每個播放器獨立的歌詞開關（每個分頁各自獨立）\n"
"• 所有已見應用程式均被記住 — 隨時重新啟用"

